
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-winter-energy-efficient-internet-01.txt'>
    <title>"Towards an Energy-Efficient Internet", Rolf Winter, Sangjin Jeong, JinHyeock Choi</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-winter-energy-efficient-internet-01.txt</link>
    <description>Climate change and cost drives all sectors of industry and society as a whole towards more energy-efficient technology, products and life styles.  The collection of Internet infrastructure and the attached devices are a large user of electrical energy and therefore of course are no exception regarding this trend.  This memo attempts to identify obstacles and more importantly technology options for an energy-efficient Internet with a focus on the protocols that are the product of the IETF.</description>
    <dc:date>2012-10-21T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
